<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>Marketing Asset Accountability · Mobile</title>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Space+Mono&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    window.MathJax = {
      tex: { inlineMath: [['\\(', '\\)'], ['$', '$']], displayMath: [['\\[', '\\]']] },
      svg: { fontCache: 'global', scale: 0.9 }
    };
  </script>
  <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-svg.js"></script>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f4f0;
      --ink: #0a0a0a;
      --mid: #555;
      --light: #9b9b9b;
      --rule: #d0cfc9;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --accent: #c94a1e;
      --soft: #ece9e0;
      --safe-bottom: env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px);
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
    }

    .deck {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .slide {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      background: var(--bg);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .slide.active {
      display: flex;
    }

    /* --- header / footer bars --- */
    .bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      gap: 8px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    .bar-bot {
      border-bottom: none;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 8px 12px;
    }

    .mono {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--mid);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .prog {
      flex: 1;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--rule);
      margin: 0 8px;
    }

    .prog-fill {
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--ink);
      transition: width .25s;
    }

    .nav-btn {
      background: none;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 6px 16px;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .15s;
      border-radius: 0;
      touch-action: manipulation;
      min-width: 80px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .nav-btn:hover {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--bg);
    }

    .nav-btn:disabled {
      opacity: .25;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .nav-btn:disabled:hover {
      background: none;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    /* scrollable body */
    .body {
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 16px 16px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      scrollbar-width: thin;
    }

    .body::-webkit-scrollbar {
      width: 3px;
    }

    .body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: var(--rule);
    }

    /* typography */
    .kicker {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--mid);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .big {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: var(--mid);
    }

    .hl {
      border-bottom: 3px solid var(--ink);
      display: inline;
    }

    .label {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: var(--mid);
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--light);
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* grids — mobile first stack */
    .g2, .g3, .g4, .timeline-grid, .step-row, .did-layout, .result-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .box {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .box.inv {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--bg);
    }

    .box.inv .label {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .55);
    }

    .strip {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 10px 12px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      align-items: center;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .strip .label {
      margin-right: 4px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 2px 8px;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .pill.inv {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--bg);
    }

    .mini-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .mini-list div {
      border-left: 2px solid var(--ink);
      padding-left: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: var(--mid);
    }

    .mini-list.inv div {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .86);
      border-left-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .55);
    }

    .stat {
      text-align: center;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 12px;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .stat .n {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 32px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .stat .s {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--mid);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    /* tables - scrollable on mobile */
    .table-wrapper {
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin: 0 -4px;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }

    table.t {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 13px;
      background: var(--white);
      min-width: 500px;
    }

    table.t th {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      color: var(--mid);
      border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 6px 8px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    table.t td {
      padding: 6px 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    table.t .n {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .rq-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-left: 6px;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: .4px;
      vertical-align: middle;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .rq-int { background: rgba(201, 74, 30, .12); color: var(--accent); border-color: rgba(201, 74, 30, .28); }
    .rq-cap { background: rgba(10, 10, 10, .08); color: var(--ink); border-color: rgba(10, 10, 10, .18); }
    .rq-het { background: rgba(85, 85, 85, .12); color: var(--mid); border-color: rgba(85, 85, 85, .18); }

    .timeline-card {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .timeline-year {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--mid);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .timeline-card h3 { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .timeline-card p, .method-copy, .plain-copy { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--mid); }

    .step-card {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 14px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .step-card .step-no { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--mid); }
    .step-card h3 { font-size: 18px; }
    .step-card p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--mid); }

    .method-flow {
      margin-top: 10px;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--rule);
      padding-top: 10px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .flow-stage {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 10px 12px;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .flow-title {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--mid);
    }

    .firm-pair { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px; }
    .firm-dot { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

    .psm-grid { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto; }
    .did-mini { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }

    .did-frame { padding: 6px; }
    svg.chart { width: 100%; height: auto; }

    .formula {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--bg);
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 12px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .result-card {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 14px;
      background: var(--white);
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .result-card .big-num {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .result-card .sub { font-size: 12px; }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(8px);
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
    }

    .reveal.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .click-hint {
      position: fixed;
      right: 12px;
      bottom: calc(12px + var(--safe-bottom));
      border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
      background: rgba(245, 244, 240, .96);
      padding: 4px 8px;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: .6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--mid);
      z-index: 20;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* --- mobile refinements (already base mobile, but ensure extra tightness) --- */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .bar { padding: 8px 12px; }
      .mono { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
      .nav-btn { padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 11px; min-width: 70px; }
      .big { font-size: 30px; }
      .kicker { font-size: 11px; }
      .body { padding: 12px 12px 16px; gap: 14px; }
      .stat .n { font-size: 28px; }
      .box, .box.inv { padding: 12px; }
      .step-card h3 { font-size: 16px; }
      .timeline-card h3 { font-size: 18px; }
      .result-card .big-num { font-size: 32px; }
      table.t { font-size: 12px; min-width: 450px; }
    }

    /* slightly larger for medium phones */
    @media (min-width: 480px) and (max-width: 700px) {
      .big { font-size: 34px; }
    }

    /* keep interactive */
    .nav-btn:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--accent); outline-offset: 2px; }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="deck">

    <!-- SLIDE 1 -->
    <div class="slide active" id="s1">
      <div class="bar">
        <span class="mono">PhD Seminar</span>
        <span class="mono">Guenther et al.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <div>
          <div class="kicker">Journal of Marketing · 2024</div>
          <div class="big">Consequences of Marketing Asset<br><span class="hl">Accountability</span>: A Natural Experiment</div>
        </div>
        <div class="box inv reveal" style="padding:16px;">
          <div class="label">One‑line setup</div>
          <div style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.4; color:rgba(255,255,255,.88);">Australia’s 2006 IFRS switch sharply restricts MA reporting → regulatory shock.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="strip reveal">
          <span class="label">Roadmap</span>
          <span class="pill">question</span><span class="pill">shock</span><span class="pill">sample</span>
          <span class="pill">groups</span><span class="pill">matching</span><span class="pill">DiD</span><span class="pill">credibility</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar bar-bot">
        <button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)" disabled>&larr; Prev</button>
        <div class="prog"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:8%"></div></div>
        <button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">Next &rarr;</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SLIDE 2 -->
    <div class="slide" id="s2">
      <div class="bar"><span class="mono">Question</span><span class="mono">2/12</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div><div class="kicker">Research question</div><div class="big" style="font-size:34px;">What happens when firms lose <span class="hl">marketing asset accountability</span>?</div></div>
        <div class="g2">
          <div class="box inv reveal"><div class="label">Object</div><div style="font-size:18px; font-weight:700;">Firms stop continuously valuing & reporting MA on balance sheet.</div></div>
          <div class="box reveal"><div class="label">Tracks</div><div class="mini-list"><div>internal: short/long-run efficiency</div><div>capital markets: cost of debt/equity, price informativeness</div><div>heterogeneity: marketing intensity</div></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar bar-bot">
        <button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)">&larr; Prev</button><div class="prog"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:15%"></div></div><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">Next &rarr;</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SLIDE 3 (empirical strategy) -->
    <div class="slide" id="s3">
      <div class="bar"><span class="mono">Strategy</span><span class="mono">3/12</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div><div class="kicker">Natural experiment</div>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;">
            <div><span class="label">treated</span><div class="big" style="font-size:30px;">used MA reporting</div></div>
            <div style="font-family:'Space Mono'; padding:6px 0; color:var(--mid);">↓ IFRS shock ↓</div>
            <div><span class="label">control</span><div class="big" style="font-size:30px;">never used MA reporting</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row">
          <div class="step-card reveal"><div class="step-no">Step 1</div><h3>Policy shock</h3><p>Reporting option removed after 2006.</p></div>
          <div class="step-card reveal"><div class="step-no">Step 2</div><h3>Groups</h3><p>Treated: prior reporters. Control: never.</p></div>
          <div class="step-card reveal"><div class="step-no">Step 3</div><h3>Match</h3><p>Propensity score matching.</p></div>
          <div class="step-card reveal"><div class="step-no">Step 4</div><h3>DiD</h3><p>Compare post-shock changes.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="box inv reveal"><div class="label">ID logic</div><div style="font-size:14px; font-weight:700;">Exogenous: firms didn't choose to lose accountability.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar bar-bot"><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)">&larr;</button><div class="prog"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:23%"></div></div><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">&rarr;</button></div>
    </div>

    <!-- SLIDE 4 sample -->
    <div class="slide" id="s4">
      <div class="bar"><span class="mono">Sample</span><span class="mono">4/12</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div><div class="kicker">Dataset</div><div class="big" style="font-size:34px;">500 ASX firms · 10 years · hand‑collected</div></div>
        <div class="g4">
          <div class="stat reveal"><div class="n">500</div><div class="s">largest ASX</div></div>
          <div class="stat reveal"><div class="n">475</div><div class="s">final firms</div></div>
          <div class="stat reveal"><div class="n">1,306</div><div class="s">MA reports</div></div>
          <div class="stat reveal"><div class="n">3,840</div><div class="s">annual reports</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="box reveal"><div class="label">Hand‑collected</div><div class="mini-list"><div>MA values reported?</div><div>type & valuation method</div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar bar-bot"><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)">&larr;</button><div class="prog"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:42%"></div></div><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">&rarr;</button></div>
    </div>

    <!-- SLIDE 5 outcomes -->
    <div class="slide" id="s5">
      <div class="bar"><span class="mono">Outcomes</span><span class="mono">5/12</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div><div class="kicker">Measurement</div><div class="big" style="font-size:32px;">Five outcomes + one moderator</div></div>
        <div class="table-wrapper"><table class="t reveal">
          <tr><th>Variable</th><th>Captures</th><th>Question</th></tr>
          <tr><td>Short‑run efficiency</td><td>immediate return</td><td><span class="rq-tag rq-int">internal</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Long‑run efficiency</td><td>customer equity / spend</td><td><span class="rq-tag rq-int">internal</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Cost of debt</td><td>lender pricing</td><td><span class="rq-tag rq-cap">capital</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Cost of equity</td><td>equity risk premium</td><td><span class="rq-tag rq-cap">capital</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Price informativeness</td><td>future earnings info</td><td><span class="rq-tag rq-cap">capital</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>Marketing intensity</td><td>centrality of mktg</td><td><span class="rq-tag rq-het">het</span></td></tr>
        </table></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar bar-bot"><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)">&larr;</button><div class="prog"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:31%"></div></div><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">&rarr;</button></div>
    </div>

    <!-- SLIDE 6 matching -->
    <div class="slide" id="s6">
      <div class="bar"><span class="mono">Matching</span><span class="mono">6/12</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div><div class="kicker">Propensity score</div><div class="big" style="font-size:30px;">Match similar counterfactuals</div></div>
        <div class="box reveal"><div class="label">Probit</div><div style="font-size:12px;">\[\text{MA reporting} = \beta_0 + \beta_1 X + \varepsilon\]</div></div>
        <div class="box inv reveal"><div class="label">Tuning</div><div class="mini-list inv"><div>5 nearest neighbors, caliper=0.09</div><div>common support enforced</div></div></div>
        <div class="box reveal"><div class="label">Balance</div><div class="mini-list"><div>size, M/B, mktg spend ✓</div><div>ROA / auditor gap → controlled</div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar bar-bot"><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)">&larr;</button><div class="prog"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:54%"></div></div><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">&rarr;</button></div>
    </div>

    <!-- SLIDE 7 DiD -->
    <div class="slide" id="s7">
      <div class="bar"><span class="mono">DiD</span><span class="mono">7/12</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div><div class="kicker">Difference‑in‑differences</div><div class="big" style="font-size:30px;">Pre/post across matched groups</div></div>
        <div class="box reveal"><div class="label">Spec</div><div style="font-size:11px;">\[\text{TE} = (E[Y_{post}|T]-E[Y_{pre}|T]) - (E[Y_{post}|C]-E[Y_{pre}|C])\]</div></div>
        <div class="did-frame reveal"><svg class="chart" viewBox="0 0 700 180"><line x1="80" y1="20" x2="80" y2="150" stroke="#0a0a0a"/><line x1="80" y1="150" x2="650" y2="150" stroke="#0a0a0a"/><line x1="360" y1="20" x2="360" y2="150" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-dasharray="5,4"/><text x="365" y="30" fill="#888" font-size="9">IFRS 2006</text><polyline points="95,80 360,84 610,86" fill="none" stroke="#9f9c94" stroke-width="3"/><polyline points="95,100 360,96 610,130" fill="none" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="3"/><line x1="617" y1="100" x2="617" y2="130" stroke="#c94a1e" stroke-width="2"/><text x="625" y="120" fill="#c94a1e" font-size="11">β</text><text x="90" y="145" fill="#555" font-size="9">Pre</text><text x="530" y="145" fill="#555" font-size="9">Post</text></svg></div>
        <div class="box inv reveal"><div class="label">Inference</div><div>SE clustered at industry. Reverse interpretation: loss of accountability → negative DiD = positive MA effect.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar bar-bot"><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)">&larr;</button><div class="prog"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:62%"></div></div><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">&rarr;</button></div>
    </div>

    <!-- SLIDE 8 parallel trends -->
    <div class="slide" id="s75">
      <div class="bar"><span class="mono">Parallel trends</span><span class="mono">8/12</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div><div class="kicker">Assumption</div><div class="big" style="font-size:34px;">Same pre‑trend</div></div>
        <div class="box inv reveal"><div class="label">Result</div><div style="font-size:20px; font-weight:700;">TR × TI insignificant (p>.13)</div><div>Parallel trends hold across all five outcomes.</div></div>
        <div class="box reveal"><div class="label">ITSA test</div><div>Augmented DiD with time trend; pre‑trend interaction not significant.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar bar-bot"><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)">&larr;</button><div class="prog"><div class="prog-fill" style="width:69%"></div></div><button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">&rarr;</button></div>
    </div>

    <!-- SLIDE 9 robustness -->
    <div class="slide" id="s8">
      <div class="bar"><span class="mono">Robustness</span><span class="mono">9/12</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div><div class="kicker">Alternatives</div><div class="big" style="font-size:32px;">Entropy balancing · synthetic control · IMR</div></div>
